    <h4>3. How To Enter?</h4>

    <article>

      <p>To join the audition, you need to post the videos under the designated hashtag and the content of the videos shall be related to any of the 5 categories. The audition will be divided into 2 rounds. </p>

      <p>The First Round of audition will start from 1/19 to 1/27. All the participants should post videos under the designated hashtag, more than 1000 winners will be chosen from each category by musical.ly team base on their performance in the first round and go to the next round.</p>

      <p>The Second Round of audition will start from 1/31 to 2/5. Winners from each category of the first round will have 6 days to post at least one video in 1 of 5 given categories. All of 200 winners will be given a creator score base on the videos they posted during Round</p>

